  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will follow ,morbidly obese subjects as they undertake weight loss before and
      after laparoscopic gastric banding, examining markers of glucose and lipid metabolism,
      adipokines and measures of body fat.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
